personal.title: Software Engineer
personal.professionalSummary: Passionate and detail-oriented Software Engineer with 2+ years of experience in developing and deploying robust applications. Skilled in full-stack development with expertise in JavaScript, Python, React, Node.js, and SQL. Proficient in Agile workflows, version control (Git), and API development. Dedicated to writing clean, efficient code and solving complex problems.

employmentHistory.description: Developed REST APIs and implemented authentication protocols such as OAuth. Enhanced security for data exposure, automated tasks to reduce manual effort, and maintained software in multiple languages, including Java and Python.
Designed and developed user-friendly interfaces with React and CSS. Improved website performance, collaborated with UX designers, and optimized responsive layouts for various devices.

educationList.description: Graduated with honors. Specialized in software engineering, data structures, and web development.
Focused on backend development, cloud computing, and API integrations.
